But there are so many more, Gollini and Djimsiti the academy players and then the likes of Gosens, Castagne, Duvan and Muriel and the whole squads, such a team spirit.

If you hunt around, see if you can find the replay of Castange's goal, there is amazing footage of from the camera at the back of the net!
